<h2 id="900">11. Automatically sending the return status</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an <a href="#en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically inform bol.com of the status of a return. bol.com requests the status of returns. The following cancellation reasons can be transferred to bol.com:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Return received</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Repaired or exchanged</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Incomplete return</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Refund without returning goods</p>
</li>
</ul>
